This is the second version of the map aim_pendulum_arena

Both galsses on the left and right side from the top area are breakable, so you can go down.

The map also has 6 awp's (3 for Counter-Terrorists, and 3 for Terrorists), but you have to find them ;D

I have tried to make a better version of the original map (aim_pendulum_arena) but still is a noob map

Give me your suggestions ;D

Enjoy and Have Fun
